column5: Hey guys/gals, I'm going to a cottage in Pointe Au Baril. Any info from some of you who have fished the area? I have a map and plan to hit up islands, points, any visible weeds, etc. Any tips and tricks would help me out, thanks.

fished it 6 or 7 years ago.  had good results then.  lots of fish, just need to find them.  typicall evening stuff for walleye.  lots of small pike in the area.  Good luck, thinking of going there again this year.
